Package: TurboIDanalysis
Type: Package
Title: Ratiometric analysis tools for proximity-based labelling applications
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christina Tsagkogianni
Maintainer: Christina Tsagkogianni <christina.tsagkogianni.2@ki.se>
Description: This package contains functions that calculate the True Positive and False Positive rates of a proximity-based labelling experiment, such as TurboID, based on user-provided true and false positive lists. The package also provides basic visualisation features to assist in the interpretation of the results.
License: MIT 
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, roxygen2
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
